QuestData.Title: Jaina's Locket
QuestData.CompletionText: Yes, $c? How can I assist you?
QuestData.RewardText: What... how did you manage to come by this!?$B$BYou have done me a great service, hero. My heart could not bear to keep this locket, but I will place an enchantment upon it that you may find useful. Do with it as you please, but do not forget those that assisted you in this monumental feat.
